ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:01:27.000Z","msg":"Pccw唔係用呢d電話亭做緊wifi熱點咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e337f7ba1f6f3c429f3014e9a610711f4bdc93f","tid":1041122,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:05:28.000Z","msg":"改做smoking room 啦"},{"pid":"64572d2267e7142f30b0c97d2a04e5c2be5e6398","tid":1041122,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"通訊局建議拆嗰千幾個根本每日收入唔夠一蚊，問咗區議會先拆到幾百個，老電不知幾想拆咁啲慳成本"},{"pid":"aeab73a9ceb47bb9f3d62a73a9dc8be6f911073e","tid":1041122,"uid":66346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />倫敦好多變咗垃圾筒"},{"pid":"b1692715b9bd137d99fe047219be352602e5e44b","tid":1041122,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a2727c81c3de794101e65548e7ab90dbf369430","tid":1041122,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"東方之豬<br />\n<br />\n紐倫港, 「港」死於1997年7月1日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9-W7ZRQPdhQ/T2GFwf75lNI/AAAAAAAAAs4/zKiqvqdNO40/s1600/U102P4T8D1139521F107DT20080120080757.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-9-W7ZRQPdhQ%2FT2GFwf75lNI%2FAAAAAAAAAs4%2FzKiqvqdNO40%2Fs1600%2FU102P4T8D1139521F107DT20080120080757.jpg&h=bebe0f2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:05:25.000Z","msg":"2019 brexit 死埋倫敦剰紐約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}